@startuml
title UC05 Client application が gateway API を呼び出す

participant "Client application" as Client
participant "Enki Gate API" as API
database "Firestore" as Firestore
collections "Cloud KMS" as KMS
participant "Upstream provider" as Provider
participant "Cloud Logging" as Logging

Client -> API: OpenAI 互換 API を呼び出す\nwith gateway token
API -> Firestore: token issuance と権限を確認
Firestore --> API: actor / credential owner / credential 情報
API -> KMS: credential 復号に必要な鍵処理を要求
KMS --> API: 復号に必要な結果
API -> Provider: provider API key を付与して request を中継
Provider --> API: response と usage metadata
API -> Logging: request / usage / policy decision を記録
API --> Client: OpenAI 互換 response を返す
@enduml
